## This project uses a custom Node server (server.ts) that hosts Socket.IO
## on /api/socket. Vercel's serverless functions cannot hold open WebSocket
## connections, so a Vercel deployment will load the UI but fail on every
## wss:// handshake.
##
## Deploy instead to Render, Fly.io, or Railway — see README for configs.
## To stop Vercel auto-deploys: Project Settings → Git → Disconnect.
*
